{"tid":1638371,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"勇武升級武力抗爭，係為左令政權唔能夠冷處理市民嘅要求","createTime":"2019-10-08T09:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:06:02.000Z","uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb022ce1d85780f8d8ff01ba8f4cce519b25549","tid":1638371,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"如果只係一星期一次和理非遊行，只要唔影響日常經濟、唔影響大財團發大財，淋病只會無視反對聲音、冷處理嚟令反對人士慢慢變返港豬。<br />\n<br />\n唯有勇武升級令到社會受影響，淋病先會考慮讓步，所以到目前雖然冇實際讓步，只係做show，但勇武的確係正確方向。<br />\n<br />\n各位和理非繼續堅守道德光環係完全ok，但唔好譴責勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位勇武，你地冇做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467dce1920359d6d3218d726854edf88ce81b1f5","tid":1638371,"uid":123440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師表示支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d736703782c5cea9e4f51d74af52180308ff4759","tid":1638371,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"正視聽！等7日？真實嘅「人權民主法案」日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ekdRyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ekdRyS</a>"},{"pid":"873f564990e9306af3b0c74af04e78f82c969ced","tid":1638371,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:06:02.000Z","msg":"支持勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}